34#ifndef _FBT_H_
35#define _FBT_H_
36
37#include "fbt_isa.h"
38
39typedef struct fbt_probe {
40 struct fbt_probe *fbtp_hashnext;
41 fbt_patchval_t *fbtp_patchpoint;
42 fbt_patchval_t fbtp_rval;
43 fbt_patchval_t fbtp_patchval;
44 fbt_patchval_t fbtp_savedval;
45 uintptr_t fbtp_roffset;
46 dtrace_id_t fbtp_id;
47 const char *fbtp_name;
48 modctl_t *fbtp_ctl;
49 int fbtp_loadcnt;
50 int fbtp_symindx;
51 struct fbt_probe *fbtp_next;
52} fbt_probe_t;
53
54struct fbt_ksyms_arg {
55 modctl_t *fka_mod;
56 void *fka_mc;
57};
58
59struct linker_file;
60struct linker_symval;
61struct trapframe;
62
63int fbt_invop(uintptr_t, struct trapframe *, uintptr_t);
64void fbt_patch_tracepoint(fbt_probe_t *, fbt_patchval_t);
65int fbt_provide_module_function(struct linker_file *, int,
66 struct linker_symval *, void *);
67int fbt_provide_module_cb(const char *, int, void *,
68 uint32_t, int, void *);
69int fbt_excluded(const char *);
70
71extern dtrace_provider_id_t fbt_id;
72extern fbt_probe_t **fbt_probetab;
73extern int fbt_probetab_mask;
74
75#define FBT_ADDR2NDX(addr) ((((uintptr_t)(addr)) >> 4) & fbt_probetab_mask)
76#define FBT_PROBETAB_SIZE 0x8000 /* 32k entries -- 128K total */
